\c 15 Kurwa kwaSamusoni navaFirisitia 1Asi nguva duku yakati yapera, panguva yokukohwa zviyo, Saâ€‘ musoni akandoshanyira mukadzi wake, akabata mbudzana; akati, "Ndinoda kupinda kumukadzi wangu mumba." Asi baba vake vakaramba kurnutendera kupinda. 2 Baba vake vakati, "Zvirokwazvo, ndakati wamuvenga kwazvo; saka ndakamupa shamwari yako. Ko mun'una wake haamupfuuri nokunaka here? Mutore hake iye panzvimbo yake." 3 Samusoni akati kwavari, "Nguva ino handingavi nemhosva kuvaFirisitia, kana ndikavaitira zvakaipa." 4 Ipapo Samusoni akandobata makava ana mazana matatu, akatora mazhenje, akabatanidza miswe miviri-miviri, ndokuisa zhenje pakati pemiswe miviri. 5 Zvino akatungidza mazhenje, ndokuaregedza, akapinda muzviyo zvavaFirisitia zvakanga zvaunganidzwa nezvakanga zvigere kukohiwa, neminda yemizambiringa neyemiorivhi. 6 Ipapo vaFirisitia vakati, "Ndianiko waita izvozvo?" Vakati,
